# Code ownership for review enforcement on critical paths
# Last matching pattern takes precedence - order general to specific

# Default: all markdown files require team review
*.md                        @Azure-Samples/edge-ai-core-dev

# Documentation directory
/docs/                      @Azure-Samples/edge-ai-core-dev

# Contributing guides
/docs/contributing/         @Azure-Samples/edge-ai-core-dev

# Component-level READMEs
/deploy/**/README.md        @Azure-Samples/edge-ai-core-dev

# Source code
/src/                       @Azure-Samples/edge-ai-core-dev

# Infrastructure as code
/deploy/                    @Azure-Samples/edge-ai-core-dev

# CI/CD workflows
/.github/workflows/         @Azure-Samples/edge-ai-core-dev

# Protect ownership file itself
/.github/CODEOWNERS         @Azure-Samples/edge-ai-core-dev
